iSuniye does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive data from users. The App solely allows users to connect to their hearing aid devices to control volume settings. No user data is processed or transmitted by the App.

Permissions Used
The App requires Bluetooth permissions to connect to hearing aids. These permissions are used solely for the purpose of establishing and maintaining a connection to the hearing aid device. No location data or any other information is collected, stored, or shared.

Third-Party Services
The App does not integrate with or rely on any third-party services or tools that collect or process user data.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in this document and made available via this URL.
